title: Malia Obama hits the bar scene in New York
text:
Modal Trigger Malia Obama Splash News 
Malia Obama has been spotted repeatedly hitting the bars now that she’s out of the White House and working in New York. 
The former first daughter, who is interning for the Weinstein Company, was seen partying in the VIP section of Up&Down Friday. 
“She arrived with heavy security, and stayed till about 2 a.m.,” says the spy. Another source adds, “She was just drinking Red Bull.” 
The young Obama, 18, has also been spotted at Soho bar the Black Lodge, attended the HBO “Girls” premiere and hit a Fashion Week after-party with J. Crew’s Jenna Lyons at Happy Ending. She also recently spent time with the high society crowd in Aspen, Colo. Share this:
